    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 101.</p><p>Tier III: Third Eye</p><p>Prerequisite: Ascended Mind</p><p>Foresight. Your great Wisdom allows you to predict the near future. You are always under the effects of the Foresight spell. This effect cannot be dispelled.</p><p>Path Connections Archmagus. Instead of the Soul of the World Heroic Perk, you can take the Erudition Perk, changing to the Archmagus path.</p><p>Herald. Instead of the Ascended Mind Heroic Perk, you can take the Words Beyond Worlds Perk, changing to the Herald path.</p></div>",
